title: Earnhardt looking for big run to continue title hopes
text: Photo: John Bazemore, AP Sprint Cup Series driver Dale Earnhardt Jr. (88) looks up at a computer screen after a practice session for Sunday's NASCAR auto race at Talladega Superspeedway Friday, Oct. 23, 2015, in Talladega. Sprint Cup Series driver Dale Earnhardt Jr. (88) looks up at a... TALLADEGA, Ala. (AP) — Dale Earnhardt Jr. has struggled in the second round of NASCAR's playoffs and needs a good run at Talladega Superspeedway to avoid elimination in the Chase for the Sprint Cup championship.
